{"tid":680684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"用心對待你，能否得到你的認同？","createTime":"2018-05-27T11:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T17:37:01.000Z","uid":180841,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fe83184e9a0eae2e9332693808cba933e9e6c7d8","tid":680684,"uid":180841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"幾個月前識左個男仔<br />\n我地日日傾計<br />\n<br />\n佢做緊野，好忙，好攰<br />\n我 好心痛佢<br />\n佢 有時同我分享佢啲野 <br />\n佢 好傻<br />\n我 發現鍾意咗佢 好想攬下佢 比佢力量<br />\n<br />\n我知佢因爲早排分咗手無咁快可以開始新戀情<br />\n而我都一樣<br />\n<br />\n但我希望我可以支持你<br />\n每夜陪你 等你講下唔開心嘅野<br />\n冇諗過同你拍拖 只想做你既開心果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都知我好撚蠢<br />\n要負評既就負啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda5ed8f23c61f1bc4d7e78840d1ca58e8205b24","tid":680684,"uid":135094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"你地邊到識 點樣識架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b3803cb58d6afa44c8d75437880ba0eec49324","tid":680684,"uid":180841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fda5ed8f23c61f1bc4d7e78840d1ca58e8205b24","tid":680684,"uid":135094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"你地邊到識 點樣識架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:08:26.000Z","msg":"網上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n現實已經見過面"},{"pid":"39b82c7d7632f477706e9504947e1a997cb921b0","tid":680684,"uid":30090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"成撚日情情塌塌 死撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"4bc8fb9c7964b40e2ff76ae3c23a044e6b11a39b","tid":680684,"uid":135094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48b3803cb58d6afa44c8d75437880ba0eec49324","tid":680684,"uid":180841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fda5ed8f23c61f1bc4d7e78840d1ca58e8205b24","t